Text: I wouldn't really recommended any expat to visit this place. It looks nice from the photos but it's quite boring and if you do not speak or understand Russian it will be quite pointless. It's in a nice and interesting location but save your 400 rubles and go somewhere else, it will be much interesting. The sculptors aren't properly cared for or looked after. While taking photos of the place, we got shouted at in Russian and my girl translated that, it's okay to photos of the place but not each other. Which seem quite absurd.
